description.displayText:
Carline really helped to clean up our space. We keep up by doing surface cleaning and vacuuming on a regular basis, but we were really in need of a deep clean by the time we found her. I think our space ended up being a bit larger than she anticipated, as she did a really great job in the first few areas, but the last few seemed quickly swiped over. 

I do think what was done was done well, and I would hire her again. I think she'll have a better understanding of the space and pace now :)
